@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
[*] --> Created
Created --> OnHold : update
OnHold --> Active : review
OnHold : entry / log message
Active --> Archived : confirm
Active : entry / log message
Archived --> Cancelled : reject
Cancelled --> Active : revert
Cancelled --> [*]
@enduml